sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as Oppi iOS
    participant Server as Oppi Server
    participant Container as Agent Container
    participant LLM as Claude API

    User->>App: Send message
    App->>Server: WebSocket: user_message
    Server->>Container: Forward to agent session
    Container->>LLM: API request (messages + tools)

    loop Agent turn
        LLM-->>Container: Stream response
        Container-->>Server: Tool calls / text deltas
        Server-->>App: WebSocket: tool_start, text_delta

        alt Tool: read_file
            Container->>Container: Read from workspace
            Container->>LLM: Tool result
        else Tool: write_file
            Container->>Container: Write to workspace
            Container-->>Server: file_changed event
            Server-->>App: WebSocket: file_changed
        else Tool: bash
            Container->>Container: Execute command
            Container->>LLM: stdout/stderr result
        else Tool: spawn_agent
            Container->>Server: Create child session
            Server->>Container: New container for child
            Container-->>App: child_spawned event
        end
    end

    LLM-->>Container: End turn (stop_reason)
    Container-->>Server: turn_complete
    Server-->>App: WebSocket: turn_complete
    App-->>User: Display rendered response

    Note over User,LLM: User can send new message or browse workspace files
